steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"e8col","text":"Make buffer and broth the day before and keep them in the fridge","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"6ll4s","text":"Day before: Grow O/N cultures of the strains of interest. Can also prepare buffers (see materials). ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"aros5","text":"Dilute overnight culture in LB broth at an OD = 0,2 and grow until OD595nm = 0.5 – 0.8 (mid-log phase). ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3734f","text":"UNTIL NOW, KEEP CULTURES ON ICE","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":31}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"evps2","text":"Spin down culture(s): transfer first to 15 mL falcon, spin 4500 RPM, 10 min, 4°C","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"o7h5","text":"In the meantime, label 2 mL tubes with strain names and add 80uL TSS buffer and 1 - 5 uL of pDNA (50-75ng). vortex and keep on ice for 10 min. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":65,"length":11}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"hhva","text":"Remove supernatant from 14 mL tubes and resuspend pellet in 1mL TSS broth(cold). Resuspend gently and keep on ice. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":64,"length":9}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"9jbqo","text":"Then transfer cells to a 2 mL tube. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"18q8k","text":"Add 200uL of bacterial culture in TSS broth to the 2 mL tubes containing pDNA in TSS buffer, Mix gently by pipetting. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":34,"length":10},{"style":"bold","offset":81,"length":10}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"6b2su","text":"Spin down (4500 RPM, 5 min), resuspend pellet in 300uL LB. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"1g0hl","text":"Spread 50 and 150ul on a plate and incubate at 30C in Chloramphenicol plates! ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":47,"length":3}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"al5uv","text":"Check plates next day for single colonies, and confirm by PCR/Sequencing. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
